==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Urticaceous
<hw>Ur`ti*ca"ceous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to a natural order (<ord>Urticaceae</ord>) of
plants, of which the nettle is the type. The order includes also the
hop, the elm, the mulberry, the fig, and many other plants.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Urtical</ent>⟦br⟧
